column4: 'title': [u'\n                    20D Too Wild To Tame Backpack Medium Backpack            ']
column14:
'desc': [u'

20D Too Wild To Tame Backpack Medium Backpack (Brown and Black) Price: Rs.1295

Backpacks are the latest trend to hit the runways and we are loving it. They are comfortable and such a practical choice when out for a long day travelling on the weekend or heading to a festival. This handbag is the perfect size to accommodate everything and still make a style statement. Accessorize with a casual top and shorts with sneakers when heading out on the weekend or a floral skirt with a denim vest and booties when planning a festival getaway. Animal print backpack with gloss finish. Single pocket in the front with magnetic clasp for fastening. Zipper on the top for fastening and ease and multiple compartments inside . Cross over straps with roller buckle for adjustment and carry ease. Dimensions of the bag are: Length (Left to Right): 11 inches. Height (Excluding the handle): 12 inches. Base Width: 4.75 inches.
']
